{"tid":1648751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得文宣咁混亂 依日都多人出其實好撚成功","createTime":"2019-10-12T10:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T03:27:09.000Z","uid":94771,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a38e62d0e1134ebf0b79a690de4a6b0215b194d8","tid":1648751,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"星期四先知，有遊行<br />\n文宣得兩日時間。<br />\n<br />\n重要文宣做唔齊，無咩人貼牆同宣傳<br />\nFacebook完全無料知道有遊行。<br />\ntwitter都少。<br />\n連登行動Post都係之前一日先有幾個。<br />\n<br />\n文宣圖極少，含路線的文宣圖更少。<br />\n<br />\n最重要係撞中咗 醫護消房感謝遊行 後尾星期五先取消咗<br />\n<br />\n做成文宣極大混亂都咁多人 <br />\n你知唔知反映咗咩<br />\n就係好多人如果知道都會出，連登仔其實唔需要怕抗爭會完<br />\n我睇得出大家都有持續落去的心<br />\n<br />\n而且唔需要屌咩休唔休息，不嬲我地一至五都係小型活動 <br />\n六，日先會有大搞"},{"pid":"9750bb5bcfb9a2149c6705bdf12f377253ecd929","tid":1648751,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1699da0959533ee7e8b642a83da90a8600528a","tid":1648751,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2a7c516f3f4cc8cf7fe0358a72dd80e6d6dcd9","tid":1648751,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xiG5kjU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxiG5kjU.jpg&h=e5a47923&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc174462fc7fa50900e594a6809b6127a14f33bf","tid":1648751,"uid":169497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"覺<br />\n失敗撚可以收皮"},{"pid":"01dde0ca8aac5667e36d94c4ea934fb09ffa9c6c","tid":1648751,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:33:56.000Z","msg":"fb ig 齊齊po<br />\npo 到大家都要知"},{"pid":"4c9290bbd4fe7c5e0b8a7e9d7ac1e7dc02b5125b","tid":1648751,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"